description.en:
memeunity is a decentralized social network (social memia, hehe)that aims to unite people through the beautiful universal language of humor. It doesn’t collect any data, it doesn’t request anything other than your email to signup, and you create a Memo (meemo) that represents your user as you have the right to not reveal any information about who you really are.
The platform aims to be a replacement for Facebook, Twitter, TikTok and YouTube, by offering more creator friendly policies that don’t screw anyone over.
